---
description: Type-aware reverse lookup of a Go symbol. Use before renaming a function or changing a signature.
argument-hint: <Symbol>
---
Run `gofasta xrefs $ARGUMENTS --json`. Symbol can be a bare name
(`UserController`), a package-qualified function
(`app/services.UserService`), or a method
(`app/services.UserService.Create`).

Report the definition location and every reference site (file,
line, enclosing function). If the result is `AMBIGUOUS_SYMBOL`,
ask the user which package they meant and re-run with the
fully-qualified form.
